A '''hoverjet''' was a form of [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmospheric]] propulsion. They were used on [[Adventurer|Verpine Adventurers]] that made a fair amount of noise.

Hover jets were also used on [[Tion Industries]]' [[Hyperfoil 1000-XTC]].<ref name="GFT">''[[Galladinium's Fantastic Technology]]''</ref>

